{"tid":1843394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幫佢開年！叫武漢人落嚟香港嘅保誠agent，可以咁投訴","createTime":"2020-01-26T07:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T09:58:10.000Z","uid":327233,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"92dbe6e148f5af03bde8b15ec9fe502ebbecfd8e","tid":1843394,"uid":327233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsbgufO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsbgufO.jpg&h=04d6ee3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDAQyHx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDAQyHx.jpg&h=89779606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.首先保誠有客戶熱線： 2281 1333<br />\n可以打過去要求投訴呢個agent <br />\n<br />\n2.其次，呢個方式先係最有效嘅：就係打電話或者寫email去「保險業監管局」投訴！<br />\n<br />\n香港所有保險公司以及保險中介人都受「保險業監管局」管束，姐係保險agent嘅牌照都係呢個機構發出嘅，呢個機構亦可以停保險agent嘅牌照。<br />\n同時呢個機構可以要求保險公司做嘢。<br />\n <br />\n原來！全港所有嘅保險agent係可以喺「持牌保險中介人登記冊 (個人)」check到資料㗎！呢啲資料本身就係公開嘅！<br />\n姐係以下呢個link：<a href=\"https://iir.ia.org.hk/#/search/individual\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiir.ia.org.hk%2F%23%2Fsearch%2Findividual&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGevo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=7d4d5a53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://iir.ia.org.hk/#/search/individual</a><br />\n<br />\n但係缺點就係，有機會check出嚟嘅係同名同姓，但唔係同一個人。<br />\n<br />\n唔緊要，我哋search佢嘅名「任煒書」，發覺得一個人叫呢個名喎，牌照號碼係IH1682，同時亦見到資料顯示係英國保誠嘅agent，得咗！<br />\n因為驚係支那人用簡體字上保險牌照，用簡體字「任炜书」再check多次發覺係冇資料嘅。咁上面check出嚟嘅資料應該冇錯。<br />\n<br />\n而「保險業監管局」嘅電話係3899 9983，<br />\n投訴電郵係 complaints@ia.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n大家可以去幫呢位「真香港人」開下年喇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疫情咁嚴重嘅情況下，仲為咗自己嘅一己之利搭路比大機會受感染嘅武漢人入香港。香港人，你忍夠未？"},{"pid":"7cff8da92463464dd5b1ca7c67c1b52e5ffbb288","tid":1843394,"uid":17551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2503c803ab7d0f0eb744a67239087fe4fa163519","tid":1843394,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:44:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaaa712d695b3a9d6e83fc9a9c6b88022a1678f8","tid":1843394,"uid":24675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:44:47.000Z","msg":"推 正人渣"},{"pid":"12d4eb05be79b305713d32fc84b01b97fdeb616e","tid":1843394,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"即刻sd爆email<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043c2c2f729c0c0de4fc5cb7beabaac5daf39eac","tid":1843394,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"044971e021bf7d2056eb97544f20c5fd479529be","tid":1843394,"uid":54364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"死仆街"},{"pid":"54442e23d4ba1af87403dda72bc9401787dce2d6","tid":1843394,"uid":43041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"炒左喇"},{"pid":"23553aab19fc8c99eb1a8bacd7479cd7da1e1b10","tid":1843394,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c95c967d317cac706fba0d9fceaebdde3d681a88","tid":1843394,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5777ba6d39645d794658fc2f1b53930ad51fbf0","tid":1843394,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"大家唔好鬧佢係仆街，人渣。佢只係智障人仕，點識分析現況，大家原諒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea671bcda745bd3889f394e8d3f226b76ad3972a","tid":1843394,"uid":201889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"54442e23d4ba1af87403dda72bc9401787dce2d6","tid":1843394,"uid":43041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"炒左喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Prudential Hong Kong<br />\n36分鐘